Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:01.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Darkness and Light!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:03.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Into the chaos of\nthe Feudal Era,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:05.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Sacred Jewel brings a\n{\i1}group of strangers together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.87,0:00:08.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}500 years across time,\ntheirdestinies are controlled{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.04,0:00:11.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}by the few remaining shards\nof the Jewel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.91,0:00:13.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Feudal Fairy Tale:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.25,0:00:14.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.15,0:00:16.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}At a coastal town,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:18.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}we meet a mysterious beauty\nwho seeks the Tetsusaiga.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:21.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This woman who is in love\nwith Sesshomaru, Inuyasha's brother,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.92,0:00:23.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}harbors a very sad secret.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.69,0:02:03.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}In orderto find the few\nremaining Sacred Jewel shards{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:06.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and to defeat ourarch-enemy Naraku,\nwe continue ourjourney.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:11.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is one other\nwho is in pursuit of Naraku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.70,0:02:13.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That is Sesshomaru,\NInuyasha's older brother.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.24,0:02:17.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sesshomaru, who is\na full-blooded demon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:18.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}cannot stand the sight of\nhalf-demon Inuyasha{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.71,0:02:20.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and considers him\na disgrace to the family.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.48,0:02:25.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha and Sesshomaru's father\nwas a great dog-demon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:27.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}who ruled over\nthe lands of the West.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:33.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The demon sword, Tetsusaiga, was\nburied in theirfather's grave.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.52,0:02:37.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that is the source of the\ntwo brothers'enmity towards each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.46,0:02:41.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There is a barrier around the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:44.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:48.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The barrierthat rejected Lord Sesshomaru\nacknowledged Inuyasha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.34,0:02:50.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:52.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I said I'd protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.81,0:02:55.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.64,0:02:58.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tetsusaiga is pulsating.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.58,0:03:02.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Reacting to Inuyasha's declaration\nthat he would protect me,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.02,0:03:05.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tetsusaiga transformed\ninto the sword of the fang.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.65,0:03:09.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sesshomaru, who lost his left arm,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:12.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}tried to wrest Tetsusaiga away\nseveral times,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:14.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}but Inuyasha has neverlost.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.27,0:03:22.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're blood brothers!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:25.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is Sesshomaru so cold-hearted\nbecause he's a demon?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:30.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still, there's a woman who loves\neven someone like Sesshomaru.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:48.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The ocean airfeels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:52.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! I can't stand this salty smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:54.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:57.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh....I{\i0} should've brought\nmy bathing suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.21,0:04:00.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look, we didn't come here to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:03.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why can't we? Nothing wrong with\nrelaxing once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.81,0:04:06.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whaddya mean by\N"once in a while"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:09.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're always relaxing and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:12.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, explain what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:17.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,By the way, Kagome, do you sense any\NSacred Jewel shards?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:20.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:26.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And no demonic aura either.\NThis area is very peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:28.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why we have to enjoy\nthis chance for a little vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:34.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, go fetch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:41.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, don't treat me like a dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:54.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is so {\i1}sad....{\i0} Dear {\i1}Princess....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:59.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, {\i1}now....{\i0} I am no longer\na princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.93,0:05:02.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am simply Sara.\NThat's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:06.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But my lady, if Asano Castle\nhadn't burned {\i1}down....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:08.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And if you hadn't fallen {\i1}ill....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.04,0:05:11.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And here, of all places!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:14.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am so, so {\i1}sad....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:19.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is what we call fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have been such a burden\nto you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:26.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you saying, my lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:31.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have been truly blessed\nto have served you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:34.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I am blessed as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.24,0:05:38.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Having been surrounded by people\nlike you and the {\i1}villagers....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:40.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,For one last {\i1}time....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.28,0:05:43.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shall {\i1}play....the{\i0} flute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.18,0:05:45.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:51.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.03,0:06:00.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.72,0:06:23.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:26.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, wait! Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.86,0:06:34.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lady Sara! Lady Sara!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:39.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have just one regret\nin {\i1}dying....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:51.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Miroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:54.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:57.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you sense it too, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.32,0:06:57.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:07:00.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on, you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:02.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ademonic {\i1}aura....{\i0} An immense one\nis {\i1}gathering....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.69,0:07:04.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demonic aura?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:10.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ademonic aura this huge....must {\i1}mean....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.80,0:07:12.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Could it be Naraku?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:15.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ademonic aura is growing,\nthat's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:17.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it's not Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:19.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And there aren't any Sacred\NJewel shards, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:20.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:23.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It doesn't involve us.\NLet's getgoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:31.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's the nunnery!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.92,0:07:34.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Something must have happened!\NLet's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:37.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! What a bother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:47.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:52.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The moment Lady Sara passed on,\nthere was a blinding light.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.44,0:07:53.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lady Sara?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:55.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The nun who lived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:08:00.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She was a kind, generous woman who\ngave us medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:03.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, this blinding {\i1}light....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.02,0:08:04.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:09.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It could be connected to the huge\ndemonic aura that accumulated earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:12.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's none of that demonic aura\nleft now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:14.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No. I don't sense it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:19.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lady {\i1}Sara....{\i0} Lady {\i1}Sara....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:22.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Herbody.... Herbody....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:24.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:27.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The bedding has a clear outline\nof a human body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:30.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right. And it's not\ncharred at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.68,0:08:33.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is where Lady Sara's body lay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.35,0:08:36.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then suddenly, it vanished\nwith the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.65,0:08:38.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vanished?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:40.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What does that mean?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:47.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, {\i1}MasterJaken....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:48.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's play tongue twisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:49.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:50.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:52.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Red Jaken, blue Jaken, gold Jaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:54.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Red Jaken, blue Jaken, gold Jaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:56.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,MasterJaken, you're pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:08:57.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Yeah!\N- One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.74,0:08:59.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Red Jaken, blue Jaken, gold Jaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:01.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Forget it.\N- Why?! Come on, say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.71,0:09:03.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.78,0:09:08.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lord Sesshomaru continues his\nsearch forNaraku,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:10.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}but we have yet to find him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:14.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}How long must we continue this?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:20.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:23.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Lord Sesshomaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:26.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh....?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:47.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It has been quite some time,\NLord Sesshomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:51.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you?\NAn acquaintance of Lord Sesshomaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:54.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am Sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.50,0:09:58.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? W-Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:01.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten about\nthe time at Asano Castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:03.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Asano {\i1}Castle....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:04.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.81,0:10:08.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The first time I saw you,\NLord Sesshomaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:11.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,was at Asano Castle\nduring those turbulent times.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:21.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My lord, it seems the enemy is planning\nto end things tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:23.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:26.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It has been one month since\nthey laid siege on our castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:30.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Provisions have run out\nand morale is low among the troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.26,0:10:35.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There is no choice but to accept death\nand make this ourgrave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:44.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everyone, listen well!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.01,0:10:49.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We will set fire to the castle\nand open the gates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:51.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is so regrettable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:53.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can we not preserve\nourdignity at least?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:56.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! Do not attempt to fight them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:58.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do whatever you must to survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:06.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My lord! My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.23,0:11:08.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?\NWhat's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.77,0:11:12.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Something seems to have attacked\nthe enemy camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.24,0:11:14.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:17.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,J-Just what are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:21.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:23.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop kidding around!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:33.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is this a miracle?!\NCould this be help sent from Heaven?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:34.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.30,0:11:36.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, Sara!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.16,0:11:38.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look at that fellow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:40.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He single-handedly broke through\nthe enemy lines
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:42.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and he's slaughtering them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:54.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:02.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord {\i1}Sesshomaru....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.96,0:12:04.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I do not know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:10.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:14.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want to help make your\nwish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:18.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wish....you{\i0} say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:21.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And when yourwish comes true,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:25.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,please accept these feelings\NI have for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:28.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will you stop this nonsense?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:32.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no way someone like you\ncan fulfill Lord Sesshomaru's wishes-!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:34.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Jaken!\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.99,0:12:38.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Stand back.\N- I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.06,0:12:42.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will fulfill yourwish,\nno matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:44.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmph....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:48.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- As you please.\N- All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.57,0:12:52.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What's {\i1}she....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.35,0:13:04.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:09.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru,\nwho is that woman, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:11.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She sure was pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:13.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! That's only make-up.\NJust make-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:17.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Geez! What can a mere human do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:19.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you blind?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:20.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:23.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That was no human.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:26.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:27.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ademon....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:31.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, perhaps originally {\i1}human....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:34.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but one who neverquite\nbecame a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:36.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:42.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder what caused that\nexplosion at that temple?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:44.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:49.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've heard that when a demonic aura\naccumulates quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:51.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,it can cause explosions like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:56.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But what puzzles me is why the body\nof that Lady Sara vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:13:59.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How could the two be related?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:02.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have this bad feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:08.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even still, it's got nothing\nto do with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:11.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Better to not stick ournoses\ninto this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:14.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wha-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.49,0:14:17.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:18.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Awhale?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:20.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, it's a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.73,0:14:23.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:24.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:33.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's that woman doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:36.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That thing is probably afterher.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:37.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:42.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shall save you right away,\nyoung lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:44.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!\NHey, Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:46.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:53.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's so predictable, that Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:58.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aww man! One can't have enough\nlives around you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:00.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing on my back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:02.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Just go!\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:04.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Awright already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:10.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:16.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.82,0:15:22.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ah! Well done, Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:34.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, take care of the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:37.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll destroy this creature\nwith my Wind Tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.64,0:15:38.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.84,0:15:41.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:42.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:48.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.25,0:15:51.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.49,0:15:57.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Look at them!\N- What happened here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:16:00.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the wrath of the Sea God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:01.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sea God?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:03.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mean that monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:08.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Herheart is beating!\NShe's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:11.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How can we save them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:15.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How else?\NWe destroy that monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:17.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it's the god of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.54,0:16:19.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who cares if it's a god!\NIt doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.05,0:16:20.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:28.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Some Sea God!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.49,0:16:31.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:40.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:42.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This {\i1}is....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:45.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Seaweed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.71,0:16:46.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:49.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It didn't work!\NThey didn't change back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.08,0:16:51.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:53.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:55.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why don't they change back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.66,0:17:09.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They look like glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:12.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even their clothes and Sango's weapon\nhave hardened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.50,0:17:15.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on? Why don't they\nrevert back to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.90,0:17:19.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Most likely, the Sea God's curse\nhas not been broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:24.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}shouldbe{\i0} grateful that\nyou saved {\i1}me....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:25.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.51,0:17:30.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I think that, perhaps, I should\nnot have been saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:31.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:33.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why are you here anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:36.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will explain in detail later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:38.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But the tide will soon come in
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:40.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and the waves will carry your\ncomrades out to sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:43.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We must hurry and\nget them away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:44.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.90,0:17:47.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can you carry them to my village?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.47,0:17:50.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just leave them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:53.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My name is Umineko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:56.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why were you tied up\nlike that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:59.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was an offering to the Sea God.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.88,0:18:00.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Offering?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:06.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Every fouryears, the sea in this area\nbecomes very rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:12.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So in my village, it is tradition to\noffer a sacrifice to the Sea God.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.87,0:18:20.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just as I {\i1}feared....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:24.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did this happen to everyone because\nwe defeated the Sea God?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.44,0:18:28.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not "we." I was the one who beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:30.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If he hadta curse anyone,\nit shoulda been me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:34.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't there any way to turn\nthem back to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:36.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:41.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe there's a chance if the shrine\nof the Sea God is destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:43.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sea God's shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:47.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Awright, take us there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.96,0:18:55.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Long ago, the Asano Clan was\nlocated here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:59.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There used to be a fine castle\non the top of the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.67,0:19:02.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.84,0:19:03.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:11.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Turning the vertical opening in the rock\nsideways would make the shrine collapse
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.72,0:19:13.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and the cliff would sink\ninto the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:14.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is how\nthe legend goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.69,0:19:19.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....{\i0} Then you shoulda just\ndestroyed the shrine in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:22.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The villagers tried once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:26.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But noteven five of the strongest\nmen could budge it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:29.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! I guess I'll give it a shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:34.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, do yourbest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:36.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's noteven moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.84,0:19:38.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why this-!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:42.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Instead of bare hands,\nwhy not try using a tool?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:45.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tool?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.55,0:19:49.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, like that sword you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:51.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.76,0:19:53.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Awright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:58.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:04.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:07.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.84,0:20:11.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Awright! I can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:13.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:16.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, that woman is suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:17.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:20.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rememberthe hardened bodies\nof Miroku and Sango?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:25.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They were both looking directly\nat her tied to the post.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.76,0:20:27.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, you're right, {\i1}but....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:33.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If it was the work of the Sea God,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:35.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,wouldn't they be looking\ntowards the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.37,0:20:37.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're {\i1}right....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.57,0:20:41.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And that woman, she laughed when\NInuyasha began moving the stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.31,0:20:44.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It must be some kind of trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:45.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It can't {\i1}be....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.88,0:20:50.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The one who did that to Miroku and Sango\nis not the Sea God, but that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:53.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that possible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.23,0:21:07.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.74,0:21:14.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.74,0:21:18.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.35,0:21:24.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.35,0:21:28.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Umineko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.99,0:21:33.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,S-Seaweed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.59,0:21:34.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.66,0:21:35.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The same as the Sea God!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.13,0:21:37.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ademon puppet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.63,0:21:40.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Both the Sea God and Umineko\nwere demon puppets!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.47,0:21:44.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.38,0:21:52.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.11,0:21:54.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, where's yourTetsusaiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.05,0:21:56.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inside the shrine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.23,0:22:08.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What {\i1}the....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.71,0:22:23.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Curse you, {\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.81,0:22:27.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tetsusaiga....{\i0} Give me the {\i1}Tetsusaiga....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.65,0:22:36.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, I take possession\nof the Tetsusaiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.56,0:22:41.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She took the Tetsusaiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.40,0:22:44.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's what she was after all along!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.90,0:22:52.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.04,0:22:59.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.68,0:23:00.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:13.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lord Sesshomaru...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.56,0:23:15.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is Lord Sesshomaru\ndoing here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.24,0:23:26.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you were behind this\nafter all, Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.24,0:23:30.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.05,0:23:40.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru.\NPlease hold him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.83,0:23:46.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.89,0:23:48.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you-!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.96,0:23:50.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop your barking, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.70,0:23:51.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wha-!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.20,0:23:54.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This has nothing to do\nwith you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.37,0:23:58.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That woman isn't one\nof Sesshomaru's cohorts?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.04,0:24:00.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess {\i1}not....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.21,0:24:04.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please take {\i1}this....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.88,0:24:07.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and put an end to Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.08,0:24:10.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are underthe wrong impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.98,0:24:16.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you really believe\nthat I desire this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.22,0:24:18.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And you do not?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.23,0:24:23.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will not accept help from one\nsuch as you to defeat Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.67,0:24:27.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please wait, Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.11,0:24:36.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord {\i1}Sesshomaru....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.54,0:24:40.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey you! Give me back\nmy Tetsusaiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.18,0:24:46.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.09,0:24:47.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's going to turn into glass!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.53,0:24:55.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, you...!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.53,0:25:00.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.97,0:25:04.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.41,0:25:08.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.07,0:25:09.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Inuyasha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.64,0:25:12.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit, she won'tget away!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.41,0:25:14.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you going afterher?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.35,0:25:18.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah! You two go and\ncheck on Miroku and Sango.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.22,0:25:19.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.25,0:25:22.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're back to normal,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.25,0:25:25.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so Miroku and the others\nshould be back to normal, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.93,0:25:27.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, will you be okay alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.33,0:25:32.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn right! I'm going to get\nback my Tetsusaiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.76,0:25:57.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This tree...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.46,0:26:04.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see... It was back then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.00,0:26:09.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shall see for myself\nif a half-demon like you
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.40,0:26:11.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,can truly wield the Tetsusaiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.91,0:26:20.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.44,0:26:47.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What is that? Ademon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.27,0:26:50.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're an eyesore!\NGet lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.58,0:26:52.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.05,0:26:55.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.38,0:26:56.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It matters not!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.68,0:26:59.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Before we take Asano Castle,\ntearthis bastard to shreds!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.46,0:27:08.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mere insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.20,0:27:10.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aghh....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.03,0:27:12.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.20,0:27:16.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.84,0:27:18.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.26,0:27:42.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn you, {\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.17,0:27:48.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give {\i1}me....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.40,0:27:52.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give me the Tetsusaiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.97,0:27:55.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.17,0:27:58.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How we searched foryou,\NLord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.08,0:28:01.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's you, Jaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.88,0:28:05.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, that despicable Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.25,0:28:11.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He not only took the {\i1}Tetsusaiga....{\i0}\nhe took your left arm, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.56,0:28:13.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lord Sesshomaru...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.19,0:28:18.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- I am so mortified!\N- {\i1}So he is called Lord Sesshomaru.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.41,0:28:29.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You remembernow?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.64,0:28:35.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, on that day, you were\nleaning against that tree and resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.55,0:28:42.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will neverforget the sight that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.92,0:28:48.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I had neverbefore seen anyone\nas handsome as {\i1}you....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.66,0:28:51.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I gazed at you\nfor a long, long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.57,0:28:59.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Later that day, I went to a nearby\npasture to pick flowers foryou.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.24,0:29:04.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I was filled with so\nmuch happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.55,0:29:11.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that demon still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.62,0:29:13.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, he is still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.29,0:29:16.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is Sara doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.69,0:29:21.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It seems that the Princess goes\nthere every day to check on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.19,0:29:25.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right, summon the troops!\NWe go to slay the demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.86,0:29:27.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.37,0:29:30.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will not have my deardaughter\nstolen by a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.74,0:29:33.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Before we shame the Asano Clan\nfor all eternity,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.51,0:29:35.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,we must take action now!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.48,0:29:43.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.68,0:29:47.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please wait, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.42,0:29:51.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru protected our castle!\NHe is our savior!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.06,0:29:53.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Out of the way, Sara!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.23,0:30:01.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My father's actions were unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.00,0:30:04.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There is no way I can\nmake amends.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.47,0:30:06.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The sound of a {\i1}flute....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.94,0:30:07.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.91,0:30:11.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought I heard a flute\non that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.28,0:30:12.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.41,0:30:16.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was this flute.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.46,0:30:30.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.63,0:30:31.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.33,0:30:37.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.50,0:30:39.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Weren't we out by the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.91,0:30:41.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll explain it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.47,0:30:44.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But before that,\nwe have to go after Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.86,0:31:02.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.30,0:31:08.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you men?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.70,0:31:10.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon, prepare to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.74,0:31:12.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.87,0:31:13.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jaken....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.71,0:31:14.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.64,0:31:15.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.28,0:31:17.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.24,0:31:19.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.15,0:31:23.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rifle squad, step up front!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.79,0:31:34.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sara....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.53,0:31:45.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It matters not!\NRifle squad, fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.27,0:31:47.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.57,0:31:49.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! Lord {\i1}Sesshomaru....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.21,0:31:56.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-The rifle squad!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.78,0:31:59.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why that {\i1}demon....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.56,0:32:12.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You foolish mortals!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.80,0:32:16.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't think you can get away\nafterdefying Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.70,0:32:18.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Retreat! Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.77,0:32:24.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru, just leave\nthe rest to me, Jaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.68,0:32:25.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let them go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.81,0:32:26.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.25,0:32:28.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The {\i1}flute....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.78,0:32:31.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The flute stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.29,0:32:34.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was shortly {\i1}afterthat....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.72,0:32:37.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Asano Castle burned\nto the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.09,0:32:42.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The one who set the castle afire was\nmy father, Soju Asano.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.23,0:32:46.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He was so frightened by\nyou, Lord Sesshomaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.23,0:32:49.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that he must have gone mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.47,0:32:56.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He chose death and went\ndown along with his castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.44,0:33:03.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I harborno ill will\ntowards you, at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.82,0:33:07.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My deranged father\nwas to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.32,0:33:11.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Afterthat, I entered a nunnery
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.29,0:33:16.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to pray forthe repose of\nmy father and his vassals.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.23,0:33:20.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But call it punishment or {\i1}fate....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.83,0:33:23.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I became ill with\na contagious {\i1}sickness....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.77,0:33:26.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and learned that my days\nwere numbered.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.61,0:33:30.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I intended to end my life
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.84,0:33:33.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,foreverkeeping secret\nmy feelings foryou.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.85,0:33:38.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But then, Inuyasha appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.42,0:33:46.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When I saw Inuyasha,\NI had second thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.19,0:33:50.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I could but live a little longer,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.33,0:33:53.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I would bearmy fangs at him,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.27,0:33:54.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and even if it meant\ndying in the process,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.07,0:33:57.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,steal the Tetsusaiga away\nfrom him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.67,0:34:03.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was the least I could do\nto atone formy father's deed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.21,0:34:09.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was then {\i1}that....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.05,0:34:18.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,many apparitions appeared\nbefore me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.33,0:34:22.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can no one else see this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.87,0:34:31.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sara, we can make your\nwish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.77,0:34:36.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your spiritual energy will\nbecome our strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.61,0:34:38.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you give us yourphysical body,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.94,0:34:43.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you will be able to kill Inuyasha\nand take possession of the Tetsusaiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.08,0:34:46.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, Sara?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.92,0:34:51.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you want to tell Sesshomaru\nhow you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.06,0:34:54.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord {\i1}Sesshomaru....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.23,0:34:58.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Beautiful Lord {\i1}Sesshomaru....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.50,0:35:04.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I had no doubts.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.24,0:35:10.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Without reservation....rather happily,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.51,0:35:13.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I gave my body and soul\nto those demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.26,0:35:32.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The overflowing spiritual {\i1}energy....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.80,0:35:36.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My soul and body which\nhad been {\i1}released....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.37,0:35:40.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.59,0:35:57.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord {\i1}Sesshomaru....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.46,0:36:02.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please acknowledge all that\NI have done until this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.83,0:36:06.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmph....{\i0} So that is your\ntrue form?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.80,0:36:08.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,True form?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.93,0:36:11.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you mean,\NLord Sesshomaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.11,0:36:14.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.21,0:36:17.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! It's {\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.01,0:36:20.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.22,0:36:27.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you're gonna get in the way,\NSesshomaru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.79,0:36:29.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You will not lay a finger\non her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.72,0:36:35.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She is none of your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.63,0:36:39.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No way!\NI'm gonna get Tetsusaiga back!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.50,0:36:41.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Blades of Blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.90,0:36:49.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Curse you, Inuyasha!\NI shall send you to yourdeath!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.51,0:36:52.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.58,0:36:56.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do not reveal any more of\nyourdisgusting self to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.78,0:36:59.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord {\i1}Sesshomaru....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.89,0:37:03.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There! It's Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.86,0:37:04.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go down, Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.89,0:37:07.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But the ones fighting {\i1}are....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.89,0:37:09.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sesshomaru and that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.96,0:37:11.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.73,0:37:17.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sesshomaru....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.97,0:37:23.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn you!\NYou've exposed {\i1}us....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.81,0:37:27.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you truly believe I would\nnot see through the disguise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.38,0:37:30.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good for you, {\i1}Sesshomaru....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.05,0:37:32.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You found us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.82,0:37:34.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's as you {\i1}thought....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.55,0:37:38.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sara was simply a medium.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.29,0:37:43.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ourtrue {\i1}aim....is{\i0} you, Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.20,0:37:48.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We made use of Inuyasha\nand took his Tetsusaiga,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.60,0:37:50.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,knowing with a certainty,\nthat you would appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.20,0:37:54.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It seems our plan was\nright on target.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.38,0:37:59.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So many demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.18,0:38:01.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.18,0:38:02.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.95,0:38:09.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.52,0:38:10.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.76,0:38:20.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Miroku!\NDon't suck up my Tetsusaiga, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.27,0:38:21.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.87,0:38:26.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.84,0:38:33.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, Inuyasha!\NThat {\i1}flute....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.11,0:38:34.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.25,0:38:38.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The nun had that flute with her\nwhen the shrine exploded!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.78,0:38:40.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So what of it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.25,0:38:44.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demon could be that nun\nfrom the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.32,0:38:46.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mean, that mass of demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.49,0:38:50.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So those demons possessed\nthat nun?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.83,0:38:51.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That must be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.26,0:38:55.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Then all we can do for her\nis destroy her!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.30,0:39:01.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This woman's spiritual energy\nhas become our power.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.81,0:39:04.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And once we absorb\nyourdemonic powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.21,0:39:06.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,we will become the\nmost powerful demon of all!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.18,0:39:09.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmph! Trash, the whole lot of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.75,0:39:12.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,L-Lord {\i1}Sesshomaru....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.62,0:39:16.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please forgive {\i1}me....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.42,0:39:20.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So she hasn't been\ncompletely taken over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.06,0:39:25.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Silence! You are now\na part of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.43,0:39:27.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Soon, you will lose all volition
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.70,0:39:30.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and you will not be able\nto move ordie.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.37,0:39:34.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All because of my {\i1}foolishness....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.64,0:39:37.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have been such a burden\nto you, Lord Sesshomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.58,0:39:39.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, I said to keep quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.05,0:39:41.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord {\i1}Sesshomaru....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.91,0:39:43.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you are {\i1}able....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.49,0:39:49.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you are {\i1}able....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.69,0:39:54.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please destroy me along\nwith the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.73,0:39:57.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.23,0:40:01.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That sword is consumed\nby anger and hatred!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.63,0:40:03.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To those of us who\nthirst forblood,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.97,0:40:06.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that sword revitalizes us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.81,0:40:11.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You cannot destroy us since\nthat sword only gives us power!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.25,0:40:23.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.76,0:40:27.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going to try!\NI want to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.63,0:40:31.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe I can purify herbody\nof those demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.76,0:40:33.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.37,0:40:39.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn you, girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.14,0:40:42.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!\NThe demons have multiplied!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.94,0:40:44.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.31,0:40:47.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if we don't do anything,\nthat woman will...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.81,0:40:51.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I cannot use my Tokijin,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.32,0:40:55.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,there is only this!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.26,0:40:58.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Tetsusaiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.56,0:41:00.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sesshomaru is wielding\nthe Tetsusaiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.76,0:41:05.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tetsusaiga, you who can destroy a hundred\ndemons in a single stroke.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.60,0:41:06.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lend me yourpower!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.85,0:41:26.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.56,0:41:37.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tetsusaiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.20,0:41:47.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! You've come back\nat last, Tetsusaiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.61,0:41:52.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now I'll show you!\NThis is my Tetsusaiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.61,0:41:55.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,K-Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.95,0:41:56.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.42,0:41:58.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry!\NYour Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.22,0:42:00.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.45,0:42:03.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind....Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.41,0:42:29.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am free at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.68,0:42:32.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord {\i1}Sesshomaru....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.02,0:42:35.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.49,0:42:43.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have no {\i1}regrets....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.90,0:42:46.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At the very {\i1}end....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.40,0:42:54.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was able to express\nmy true {\i1}feelings....to{\i0} you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.32,0:43:12.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go and play your flute\nin the otherworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.63,0:43:18.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder what {\i1}happened....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.30,0:43:21.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I feel {\i1}so....so{\i0} sorry forher.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.40,0:43:22.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.24,0:43:26.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, I believe this is forthe best.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.44,0:43:29.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Was this lady saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.24,0:43:34.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can tell from her\npeaceful expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.11,0:43:38.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sesshomaru saved Lady {\i1}Sara....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.35,0:43:41.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! As if Sesshomaru would\ndo such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.99,0:43:45.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He was just passing through\nlike the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.96,0:43:46.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.34,0:44:00.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where could he have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.37,0:44:05.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.78,0:44:09.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where have you been,\NLord Sesshomaru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.11,0:44:11.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.52,0:44:13.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nowhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.29,0:44:17.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, don't be so {\i1}vague....{\i0}\NLord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.79,0:44:19.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Let's go.\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.79,0:44:21.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Lord Sesshomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.93,0:44:24.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru, where...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.50,0:46:06.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What did you say, Hachi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.46,0:46:07.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,MasterMushin is going to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.73,0:46:10.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. It's regrettable,\nbut I've seen him!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.50,0:46:12.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mushin? You mean, the monk\nwho raised Miroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.20,0:46:14.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look, everyone dies eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.91,0:46:16.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No sense getting sentimental\nabout it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.31,0:46:17.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.21,0:46:18.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, Inuyasha is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.38,0:46:21.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whatever lives must someday die.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.28,0:46:22.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.25,0:46:24.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't there anything we can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.62,0:46:28.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"The Last Banquet of Miroku's Master"
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.35,0:46:31.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let us give him a fine send-off\nto the otherworld.
